This Project Comprises of Using Two Different Repositories :
1) batman-adv :
2) babeld     :

So in order to run this new hybrid protocol, 
  1)Download the repo of Batman-adv.
  2)Downnload the modified babeld repository from my repository.
  3)Download the Script Files.
  4)You should have GnuPlot and other dependencied installed.
  5)Make sure that your NIC supports Ad-Hoc Mode.
  6)Run the Scripts and observe the graphs
  
